<!-- Main Body Section -->
<main class="flex-shrink-0 pt-3 mt-5" id="mainContactStyle">
    <div class="container col-xxl-8 px-4">
        <div class="row g-5 row-cols-1 row-cols-lg-2">
            <div class="col order-last order-lg-first">
                <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold lh-1 mb-3 app-name">Project WhatsYourAddy: A coding project</h1>
                <h4 class="lead">
                    The FizzBuzz algorithm is a classic coding test given in coding interviews. Pseudo Code: <br><br>
                        1. Print integers 1 to N. <br>
                        2. Print “Fizzy” if an integer is divisible by the fizzy Value.<br>
                        3. Print “Buzz” if an integer is divisible by the buzz Value.<br>
                        4. Print “FizzBuzz” if an integer is divisible by both fizzy Value and buzz Value.
                </h4>
                <h4 class="lead">
                    I Built this application using the following tech stack:
                </h4>
                <ul class="fa-ul pt-2 tech-stack">
                    <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fas fa-check-square"></i></span>CSS and BootStrap Layouts</li>
                    <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fas fa-check-square"></i></span>C# Loops</li>
                    <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fas fa-check-square"></i></span>C#  Classes</li>
                    <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fas fa-check-square"></i></span>C# & ASP.NET MVC</li>
                    <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fas fa-check-square"></i></span>C# If|Then|Else</li>
                    <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fas fa-check-square"></i></span>C# Boolen Logic</li>
                    <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fas fa-check-square"></i></span>C# Control Flow</li>
                </ul>
                <div>
                    <a class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-lg px-4 me-md-2" type="button" asp-controller="Contacts" asp-action="index">Try It Out</a>
                </div>
